QuestData.Title: Taragaman the Hungerer
QuestData.Description: The Searing Blade has managed to summon a foul demon they call Taragaman the Hungerer to lead the first attack in their takeover of Orgrimmar!$B$BMake haste and slay Taragaman in the name of the Warchief! Lok'tar ogar!
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Time to feed him a heaping plate of pain.
QuestData.CompletionText: If Taragaman is dead, show me his heart.
